column6: THOR: THE TENTH REALM - Thanks to the events of ORIGINAL SIN, the deepest secret of the Nine Realms is revealed... a Tenth Realm! - Thor and Loki embark on a quest to discover this strange new world -- and the sister Thor never knew he had... Angela! - But can Loki be trusted? And will brother and sister murder each other before the truth comes out?
column8: | writer:Jason Aaron | writer:Al Ewing | penciller (cover):Simone Bianchi | artist:Lee Garbett
